data.description: Beautiful view home in the highly desirable Ledgewood community in Coupeville. With recent renovations including updated bathrooms, upgraded primary suite, extended patio and fire pit, and a new garden area, this move in ready home also comes complete with amazing mountain and water views! Large primary on the main level, skylights to let ample light in year-round, and two extra bedrooms upstairs give you plenty of room for guests and entertaining. Community features include private beach access, a community club house, tennis courts, and open park areas. Enjoy your new spacious living and kitchen areas from your very own piece of the amazing PNW!
